using nothing but a toothpick and some olive oil. In order to fetch these edible sea creatures,<br/>
without being injured by perilous waves, he is hoisted down by rope and harness by the two fellow band members, Luke and Liam,<br/>
in what is called a ‘counter-balance abseil’. <br/>
Afterwards they drink warm, brown beer and inhale sea breeze. <br/>
<br/>
In this way, the music is made.<br/>
<br/>
After seeing such a site, Iggy Pop left the review, ‘Decius are a strange underground motley collection of weird-looking guys… that I kind of like!’<br/>
<br/>
